{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"2":"The Book of the Prayer"},"section_detail":{"2":{"hadithnumber_first":667,"hadithnumber_last":705,"arabicnumber_first":667,"arabicnumber_last":705}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":683,"arabicnumber":683,"text":"حدثنا ابو بكر بن ابي شيبة، حدثنا سفيان بن عيينة، عن الزهري، عن عروة، عن عايشة، قالت صلى النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم العصر والشمس في حجرتي لم يظهرها الفىء بعد","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih - Bukhari And Muslim"}],"reference":{"book":2,"hadith":17}}]}